{"_path":"/maps/_visual/visual","_dir":"_visual","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"可视化","description":"可视化技术、信息设计与地理信息系统","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"子领域"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"子领域"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_visual/info-design/info-design"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"信息设计"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_visual/visualization/visualization"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可视化技术"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_visual/gis/gis"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GIS"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概述"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概述"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可视化领域涵盖三个核心方向："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"信息设计"}]},{"type":"text","value":"关注如何有效地展示和传达信息。它不仅涉及形状、色彩、容器等视觉映像，还涉及视角、情绪、隐喻等心理层面因素。设计师作为信息和受众之间的桥梁，需要将深奥复杂的信息转化为能被受众理解的形式，目标是实现清晰、准确而高效的传达。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可视化技术"}]},{"type":"text","value":"是将数据转换为可视化图形的技术手段，是数据分析的重要工具。包括各种图表、图形的实现原理，如模糊效果、视错觉等视觉技术的实现，以及数据可视化系统的搭建方法。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"**地理信息系统（GIS）**是一种用于捕获、存储、管理、分析和展示地理空间数据的计算机系统。GIS 技术广泛应用于地图制作、空间分析、城市规划、环境监测等领域，为空间数据的可视化和分析提供了强大的工具支持。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"子领域","depth":2,"text":"子领域"},{"id":"概述","depth":2,"text":"概述"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_visual:visual.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_visual/visual.md","_stem":"6.maps/_visual/visual","_extension":"md"}